OL,6,FDaniel Aldridge, MP for Weston-super-
OL,7,FMare hasn't indicated how he will
OL,8,Fvote, but has similarly said: "I did
OL,9,Fnot come into politics to impose this
OL,10,Fon the most vulnerable in our
OL,11,Fsociety... I have serious concerns
OL,12,Fabout how these changes could affect
OL,13,Fchildren and disabled people in
OL,14,FWeston, Worle, and our villages."
