OL,3,CWest Country Labour MPs divided over
OL,4,Cgovernment cuts to benefits
OL,6,FThe impact assessment also shows that
OL,7,Fthe decision to tighten eligibility
OL,8,Ffor Personal Independence Payments
OL,9,F(Pip) will affect 800,000 disabled
OL,10,Fpeople, who will lose an average of
OL,11,F#4,500 a year.
OL,13,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,14,FKendall announced last week that fewer
OL,15,Fpeople will be eligible for Pip, with
OL,16,Fclaimants having to prove more severe
OL,17,Fdifficulties in order to qualify.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
