OL,3,CWest Country Labour MPs divided over
OL,4,Cgovernment cuts to benefits
OL,6,FThe two Labour MPs in our region
OL,7,Faren't the only ones expressing
OL,8,Fconcern about the changes, and I
OL,9,Funderstand a number from across the
OL,10,FSouth West have written to Kendall in
OL,11,Fa bid to get some of the cuts reversed.
OL,13,F"I know many colleagues are similarly
OL,14,Fconcerned about these proposed changes
OL,15,Fand we will continue to make the case
OL,16,Fto ministers that we should find a
OL,17,Fbetter way," said Daniel Aldridge.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
