OL,3,CWest Country Labour MPs divided over
OL,4,Cgovernment cuts to benefits
OL,6,F"However, while I agree with the
OL,7,Fsignificant #1 billion investment in
OL,8,Fthe Pathways to Work offer, the 'right
OL,9,Fto try' policy and the measures
OL,10,Fintroduced to protect those with
OL,11,Fchronic, lifelong disabilities, I,
OL,12,Flike many colleagues, have concluded
OL,13,Fthat these measures, as they stand,
OL,14,Fare likely to push large numbers of
OL,15,Fpeople in my constituency further into
OL,16,Fpoverty.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
